Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103166,105043}Hurry up, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106336,108171}Wait for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109672,111591}Are we climbing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:56.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111591,116429}Seriously, you're chickening out now?\NYou yourself told me about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:01.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116429,121476}Dad told me that he had found it\Nwhen he was a kid, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:02.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121476,122769}I wasn't prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:03.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122769,123936}It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125396,127940}See? Lassie wants us\Nto climb with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:09.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128775,129984}Don't let go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129984,131444}Of course… I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148252,149420}We're so high up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149420,150755}We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:41.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159597,161140}We're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:44.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161140,164018}This is the highest rock\Nin all of Greenall Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171984,173569}Amazing…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176072,179325}To think it's all naturally formed.\NIt's like a castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179325,181119}The cave is so big…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183371,186999}This rock looks like a king's throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:10.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186999,190920}There's even light in here.\NOne can read books in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190920,193297}If we climb here,\Nwe can go even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193297,194132}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194799,198469}You want to go even further?\NI'm good where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:22.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198469,202682}Yep. If possible,\NI'd like to see the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202682,205643}Count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209605,212817}Hey, John!\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214110,215945}Hey! John!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215945,217947}I can see the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217947,219157}Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225538,228708}This is the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235339,237967}Colin! The sky looks strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237967,239260}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:01.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239260,241763}The clouds are all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241763,243222}What's more…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243431,245767}What's with that black line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271459,272460}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272460,274128}You're still at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274128,275546}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:41.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276881,281177}What I meant to ask is, where did you keep\Nthat weather meter all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281177,283679}Didn't we get it as a gift\Nfor our wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:47.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283679,287350}It's called "barometer".\NI kept it in my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287350,289727}Barometer, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:53.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289727,293648}Oh, well. It's used for weather forecast,\Nso I might as well call it a "weather meter".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293648,295525}What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295525,299654}Barometers can only measure\Nair pressure, no less and no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299654,301989}I think John will like it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:07.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301989,307411}I can't believe you still have things\Nthat John broke as a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307411,310331}Your desk is like a jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310331,312750}What else do you hide there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312750,314710}Oh? This is weird…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314710,316003}What's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316003,319257}Well, I'm fairly sure I had it fixed…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319257,321968}But the readings are way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:25.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321968,325763}My goodness. Does it mean\Nthat we can expect a storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326389,328391}Looks like it's still broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:32.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328391,332520}Not even a single cloud in sight.\NThere's no way a storm would be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332520,335022}Oh, I forgot about the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:38.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335022,338526}I don't think you can rely on\Nsuch contraptions to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338818,340528}But John should…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365553,367471}What on earth was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367471,368264}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:22.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378858,382862}Hey! Grandpa Bansen!\NHow is it going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:27.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382862,387867}You goofball! You're thirty years\Ntoo old to call me Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:34.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388075,394457}Stop grumbling and see if it can\Nwithstand heavy winds or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394457,395708}All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398085,399837}All he does well\Nis holding the liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399837,402882}Ah, you won't like it, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:46.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403257,406928}All the bolts at the top\Nhave completely rusted through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:47.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406928,407803}Here, see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413267,415519}Are all of them like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:07:01.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415519,421233}Well, this tower is as old\Nas the pyramids. You can't blame it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:05.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421233,425529}I think it will collapse\Nwith the first bigger storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:09.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426364,429951}I was afraid he'd say that.\NThat's a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429951,432703}What are we going to do?\NDo we tell the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432703,435331}No! I'll go and tell Sam first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435331,437375}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:21.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437375,441128}It's not like we can rely\Non the manager, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441128,442505}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:26.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442505,446467}Whatever we do, we better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463401,465736}I have to get home\Nbefore it starts raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466445,469323}Lassie?\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470825,473327}Hey, girl!\NWe're going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:02.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477873,482044}{\i1}Due to a development of a low pressure\Nsystem, extreme caution is advised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482044,484046}{\i1}Now, the top hits for this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489635,492638}Welcome back.\NHow was the weather outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492638,496142}There are big ominous clouds.\NThe wind is so strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496142,498686}Dad, there's a gale…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509113,511866}Hey there, John!\NYou've grown big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511866,513868}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513868,516787}Why do you look so troubled?\NDid you have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:40.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516787,520416}A fight?\NYou mean, me with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:43.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520416,523127}I came to ask Sam for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:43.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523127,523878}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523878,526505}I wonder if we could use\Nwires for support.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:50.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526505,530801}That's all we can do. Let's get to it\Nwhile the wind is still relatively calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530801,532386}Let's go. I'll get the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532386,533345}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538350,540978}Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:06.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540978,546233}The scaffolding around the\Nmine's shaft is about to turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546233,547443}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:11.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547443,551363}Is it really going to fall?\NIf it did…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:17.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551363,557286}Maybe the big wheel at the top of it\Nwill fall and roll toward our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557286,560956}Makes you wonder what's going\Nto happen next, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560956,563501}Uh… Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:28.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565252,568589}It'll be fine.\NIt won't fall so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568589,571425}Dad and his boys are going\Nto do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:37.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573719,577139}My hat…\NWait! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:42.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577389,582645}I wonder sometimes if he really\Nis so reliable, or if it's all hooey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583521,585564}It'll be fine, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:50.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587233,590653}The tower won't turn over\Nfrom this wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:57.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593030,597034}It's only evening,\Nand the sky is pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:01.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597034,601372}Where did the sun go?\NWas it swept by the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603082,604416}Sandy's house…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605126,607419}I wonder how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:14.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610589,614009}I hate thunder!\NGet away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630109,632027}John? John!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632444,634530}John, come here for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634530,636198}What's up, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636198,637700}I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637700,639410}What? In this storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639410,640870}Sorry about that, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:45.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640870,645166}Old Morton's heart\Nis playing pranks on him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645166,646417}Let's go, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646417,647168}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647168,648878}John, take care of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:49.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648878,649712}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656010,657303}Are you okay, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:01.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658429,661098}Please, Doctor, get off my foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:04.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661098,664310}Damn it to hell.\NThese cost us a pretty penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:20.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675446,680242}I sure don't envy them. Too bad\Nthe sick can't wait till the storm passes.
Comment: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:24.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:684705,684705}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701555,703515}It's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:54.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708896,714193}The whole neighborhood is dark.\NLooks like the power's out for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716612,718447}What's going on?\NAre you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:03.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720032,723827}Just a moment.\NLet's see… Matches. Matches…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723827,727414}Oh? It's so dark.\NI can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728332,730125}Oh, here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:16.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733379,736215}It's a bit merrier now, right, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742805,744181}Is it the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745641,747017}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754108,756735}Sandy's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756735,758779}Boy, you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:43.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758779,763534}We lost a couple of sheep and I went out\Nto look for it, but it was too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763534,764994}Can I stay here for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768956,772084}How bad is it outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772084,774795}It's not that bad, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:13:00.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774795,780926}But my grandfather said there was\Na more severe storm going to Yorkshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780926,782344}Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782970,785139}It goes on and off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785139,788350}I'm afraid that\Nthe worst is yet to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:15.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791687,795149}All right, I'm going home\Nwhile I still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795149,796483}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802531,804908}Is it getting even worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:57.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831310,837024}{\i1}Low pressure moves towards North Yorkshire\Nand the intensity of the wind increases.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:01.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837024,841195}{\i1}We advise everyone to stay inside\Nor find a shelter—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842363,844531}The power is out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844531,846992}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850162,851455}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:19.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855250,859963}It'll be too difficult\Nfor Mom to get back…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861256,864968}But Dr. Hopper may not be able\Nto do anything without the syringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865677,867388}What to do, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867388,869390}There's such a terrible storm outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870099,873477}There is no one outside.\NNot a single person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874561,875979}Still…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:39.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875979,879274}I have to deliver that syringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:44.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879900,884613}If you really don't want to go,\Nyou can stay inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:50.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884613,890786}I wonder how is it going to feel\Nto run in such a terrible storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892746,894873}Let's go, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:15:00.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894873,900838}Listen, we're headed straight towards\Nthe bridge, then to Mr. Morton's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901213,902714}Here goes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:25.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921525,925696}I know! I want to go\Nin that direction myself, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943338,945924}Smarty!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949887,950846}You're soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953432,955434}You'll be fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955434,958270}Stay in our house\Nuntil the storm is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960022,962232}All right, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962232,963734}Let's go, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:15.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970949,975412}Damn! I'm not getting\Nany closer to Mr. Morton's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977498,978624}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:45.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000979,1005859}We must pass this square,\Nbut the wind is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006193,1007611}We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025796,1027714}Heck, the syringe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:34.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049903,1054825}Back to square one.\NHow are we supposed to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055158,1056577}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076054,1078390}How do you feel?\NDoes it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078390,1080517}Yeah. Please,\Ncan't you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:04.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080517,1084563}You'll be fine. You've taken\Nyour medicine and you ate well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084563,1086898}Your life is not in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:10.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086898,1090068}It hurts… It hurts so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:14.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090068,1094573}Get it together!\NYou're too big for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:19.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094573,1099453}Yes, but the pain\Nreally is unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099453,1100704}For heaven's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100704,1103999}It would be better\Nif he took some sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:30.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103999,1110464}There's not much we can do. The syringe\Nfell out of my bag at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:35.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111381,1115010}Please, Doctor,\Ngive me some painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115010,1116887}Don't just rely on medication!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116887,1120057}Can't you handle a little pain\Nwith your own strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:45.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120057,1125479}May Lord not hear me through this storm,\Nbut you've been always such a spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:49.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125979,1129399}We can't get back to get the syringe.\NNot in this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129399,1130984}Let's observe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130984,1131985}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:08.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144498,1148001}Look at all that water.\NThe bridge's gonna get flooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152005,1154049}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155550,1158053}It's Sandy's sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158345,1161181}It can't stay there,\Nor it'll drown in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:28.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165018,1168105}Wait for me, I'm gonna save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:41.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177072,1181535}His pulse is getting weak.\NHe may have had a really bad attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181535,1182619}Mrs. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182619,1183203}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183203,1184454}Take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184454,1185580}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185580,1187833}I'm going to get the syringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187833,1189376}In that storm, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189376,1190502}Out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:54.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191670,1194297}So you don't think\Nit's possible in this storm…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194297,1195590}It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:59.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195590,1199010}The patient absolutely\Nneeds your treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199010,1200804}I will go instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200804,1202431}Mrs. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:05.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202431,1205517}I can't let you go\Nunder these circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205517,1207352}It's all my fault to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207352,1208228}No, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208228,1210230}It doesn't matter who goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210230,1212357}Just please, make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:16.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212357,1216069}H-He's right.\NSo what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216069,1217279}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217279,1218530}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218947,1220532}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221867,1223076}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:29.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227247,1229541}Thank goodness, we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264618,1266703}Seems like it's going to\Nhold up for time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277839,1279174}You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279174,1280383}It's beyond awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280383,1283512}We couldn't show you\Nit before because of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:28.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286389,1288433}This is our rocky castle.
Comment: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:56.50,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1316503,1316503}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:03.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319297,1323218}{\i1}The snow came. One of my friends'\Nmufflers was stolen at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:08.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323218,1328265}{\i1}Everyone is thinking\Nthat the culprit is Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:10.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328265,1330976}{\i1}But you're innocent,\Nright, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330976,1333979}{\i1}Next episode:\N"Catch The Muffler Thief".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333979,1335480}{\i1}Be sure to watch!
